{"tid":294124,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"邊份工好D","createTime":"2017-06-22T16:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T16:39:37.000Z","uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9dd21c8370037fbb376bdc8c48ea828bfc52ad","tid":294124,"uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"之前上網見到實惠請理貨員/收銀員（佢果度係咁寫，但唔知佢請邊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）時薪佢冇寫，但都算屋企<br />\n第二份就係baleno就50蚊一個鐘，都係近屋企，但就冇咩類似經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三份就係做酒店既類似上菜果D，但聽佢講話要set場，同搞開會既野（因為人地介紹，所以都未問到好多野住）佢有兩餐食同人工就六十幾，但就係旺角，唔近屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲做緊or就快返頭兩份工呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以簡單講下同你地會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85c80f56ce46dc602f97e52913e68da72e29520","tid":294124,"uid":29399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"三份都係狗屎垃圾都返到既工有咩所謂<br />\n唔鍾意咪轉"}]}